Now she is willing to preserve the peace.

0:03:57.670,0:03:59.506
Don't talk disrespectfully about the Empress.

0:04:12.810,0:04:17.920
I thank Your Majesty for granting my wish,
personally tying a talisman pouch for me.

0:04:18.940,0:04:21.220
I am the Empress. It is my duty.

0:04:22.610,0:04:24.171
As a rule, it is your duty.

0:04:24.530,0:04:28.860
But in terms of feelings, Your Majesty most likely resents me.

0:04:33.910,0:04:35.580
I gifted you the Guanyin statue

0:04:35.580,0:04:37.745
hoping to bring peace to your heart.

0:04:38.014,0:04:42.760
The most important thing now is to
 give birth to this heir for His Majesty.

0:04:46.170,0:04:50.440
Whether my child can survive is 
entirely up to Your Majesty, not I.

0:04:52.220,0:04:53.474
Why is that?

0:04:53.930,0:04:55.222
Is that not true?

0:04:57.180,0:04:59.550
If Your Majesty so wishes, an heir can live.

0:04:59.890,0:05:02.227
But both mother and child can be ruined if their lives 
run counter to Your Majesty's wishes.

0:05:02.520,0:05:03.600
For so many years,

0:05:03.650,0:05:05.640
Your Majesty has ruled the harem in this way.

0:05:06.980,0:05:08.440
I'm truly frightened

0:05:08.860,0:05:10.796
that if, one day, I offend Your Majesty,

0:05:11.320,0:05:14.200
I won't be able to save the baby in my belly.

0:05:14.310,0:05:16.570
Nonsense! You dare slander me?

0:05:16.870,0:05:17.761
Slander?

0:05:19.520,0:05:20.234
Let go!

0:05:20.234,0:05:21.957
Do you dare swear to the divine beings

0:05:23.290,0:05:25.181
that you've never harmed any imperial heirs?

0:05:25.492,0:05:26.742
Any concubines?

0:05:26.920,0:05:28.660
And that you've never harmed me?

0:05:29.010,0:05:32.168
