Why should I swear at your command?

0:05:32.890,0:05:33.720
Let go!

0:05:33.890,0:05:34.800
You're scared, aren't you?

0:05:36.560,0:05:38.080
Why did Consort Austuce commit suicide?

0:05:39.140,0:05:40.831
Why did Concubine Paix lose her fertility?

0:05:41.560,0:05:42.959
Noble Lady Fuca's miscarriage.

0:05:43.940,0:05:45.800
And the loss of my first child.

0:05:47.150,0:05:49.268
You've done so many wicked things.

0:05:49.490,0:05:51.190
In your heart, you know full well!

0:06:01.910,0:06:02.920
How did this happen?

0:06:02.920,0:06:03.796
What happened to Her Highness?

0:06:06.460,0:06:07.680
What's happened to Her Highness?

0:06:08.250,0:06:09.141
Your Highness!

0:06:10.210,0:06:11.040
What's wrong?

0:06:14.050,0:06:15.243
Your Highness, what happened?

0:06:15.720,0:06:16.630
We need help!

0:06:16.800,0:06:18.540
Your Highness!

0:06:18.810,0:06:20.770
- Huan Huan!
- Your Majesty, Her Highness has fainted!

0:06:21.020,0:06:22.084
Call an imperial doctor!

0:06:22.084,0:06:22.810
- Yes!
- Go quickly!

0:06:23.060,0:06:23.800
Huan Huan!

0:06:24.020,0:06:25.003
Doctors!

0:06:25.730,0:06:27.890
Somebody get an imperial doctor!

0:06:28.192,0:06:30.192
Quickly get an imperial doctor!

0:06:32.040,0:06:33.080
Her Highness...

0:06:41.720,0:06:43.221
Your Highness!

0:06:43.689,0:06:45.660
Your Majesty, Her Highness is awake.

0:06:55.930,0:06:58.264
Noble Consort Lumière, you're awake.

0:06:59.430,0:07:01.420
Noble Consort Lumière, you should refrain from grief.

0:07:01.840,0:07:03.360
You will have another child someday.

0:07:05.040,0:07:07.333
I will have another child someday...

0:07:08.000,0:07:10.951
How can Your Majesty treat my child
as if he were a withered weed,

0:07:11.700,0:07:14.150
offering words of such faint comfort?

0:07:16.240,0:07:17.353
Your Majesty,

0:07:18.640,0:07:20.593
no matter how much you resent me,

0:07:21.800,0:07:24.150
why did you have to harm my child?

0:07:26.480,0:07:29.270
Ridiculous! When have I ever harmed your child?

0:07:30.790,0:07:33.620
Your Majesty... Your Majesty...

0:07:35.010,0:07:37.336
My child is gone,

0:07:38.600,0:07:40.991
not because I was careless.

0:07:42.560,0:07:44.000
It was Her Majesty...

0:07:45.400,0:07:47.460
She had a quarrel with me ...

0:07:48.640,0:07:50.430
and she pushed me.

0:07:56.400,0:08:00.533
Your Majesty, there are signs of Her Highness
being struck heavily on the stomach.

0:08:00.920,0:08:02.480
The imperial doctors can testify to that.

0:08:03.000,0:08:05.020
Someone must have pushed Her Highness forcefully.

0:08:05.640,0:08:08.020
Besides, the fetus in her belly has always been healthy.

0:08:08.320,0:08:11.515
Your Majesty must have felt the fetal movement often.

0:08:12.000,0:08:15.440
Were it not for the accident, a miscarriage would never have happened.

0:08:18.400,0:08:19.360
Empress,

0:08:20.260,0:08:24.238
only you and Noble Consort Lumière were inside the chamber!

0:08:25.400,0:08:26.410
Your Majesty...

0:08:34.200,0:08:35.151
You,

0:08:37.000,0:08:38.202
and you.

0:08:38.750,0:08:40.753
You two were right outside by the door.

0:08:41.120,0:08:42.520
Did you see anything?

0:08:42.920,0:08:46.039
The Imperial Consort and I were conversing outside the chamber.

0:08:46.039,0:08:48.052
We did not see anything, however...

0:08:49.920,0:08:55.441
However, the Imperial Consort and I did hear from inside the chamber

0:08:55.802,0:08:58.880
that Her Majesty and Noble Consort Lumière seemed to be having a dispute.

0:08:59.800,0:09:01.064
It's true, Your Majesty.

0:09:01.590,0:09:03.550
Her Majesty and Noble Consort Lumière were arguing.

0:09:03.550,0:09:05.120
We didn't dare to barge in.

0:09:05.360,0:09:09.043
I heard Noble Consort Lumière utter words like "afraid" and "terrified".

0:09:09.810,0:09:13.500
And Her Majesty told Noble Consort Lumière
to know her place and behave properly.

0:09:13.690,0:09:16.440
I did not make out anything else.

0:09:18.520,0:09:22.320
I saw with my own eyes, along with many pairs of eyes here,

0:09:23.410,0:09:27.360
When Noble Consort Lumière was injured and fainted,
only the Empress was at her side.

0:09:28.000,0:09:29.040
Your Majesty...

0:09:30.000,0:09:32.640
Her Majesty resents me for being favored by Your Majesty.

0:09:33.080,0:09:35.560
She believes that I harbor disrespect in my heart.

0:09:35.600,0:09:37.040
She rebuked me for it...

0:09:37.946,0:09:42.200
and pushed me in fierce anger.

0:09:43.280,0:09:45.200
Noble Consort Lumière was pestering and harassing me.

0:09:45.200,0:09:46.632
She grabbed my hand,

0:09:46.960,0:09:49.054
and I had to use strength to get myself away.

0:09:49.280,0:09:51.168
I did not push Noble Consort Lumière!

0:09:54.360,0:09:55.890
According to what you said,

0:09:56.080,0:09:58.800
it was Noble Consort Lumière who pushed herself over.

0:09:59.600,0:10:00.930
Your Majesty, I don't understand

0:10:01.000,0:10:03.240
why Noble Consort Lumière would pester Your Majesty.

0:10:03.990,0:10:05.640
Noble Consort Lumière is modest and prudent.

0:10:05.680,0:10:09.062
She follows the doctor's advice
and takes every bowl of the prenatal tonics on time.

0:10:09.280,0:10:13.280
For all these years, Noble Consort Lumière
has treated Your Majesty with diligence and deference.

0:10:14.440,0:10:17.083
Even if she displeased Your Majesty with certain words,

0:10:17.083,0:10:18.853
Your Majesty should be forgiving towards her.

0:10:19.440,0:10:23.720
Or at least give consideration to the imperial heir in her belly.

0:10:24.320,0:10:26.831
You said Noble Consort Lumière was pestering and harassing you.

0:10:27.240,0:10:31.175
How exactly did she disrespect you?

0:10:32.400,0:10:36.467
There were only the two of us in the chamber.

0:10:37.360,0:10:39.778
I know I can hardly defend myself even with a hundred mouths.

0:10:40.000,0:10:42.280
However, I was involved in this incident

0:10:42.280,0:10:45.280
because someone had their heart set on framing me.

0:10:46.200,0:10:48.520
You feel like you can't defend yourself even with a hundred mouths.

0:10:48.520,0:10:51.640
I feel that I can't understand this even with a hundred brains.

0:10:52.840,0:10:56.160
There were only the two of you inside and you had an argument.

0:10:57.520,0:10:59.120
I've seen with my own eyes

0:10:59.120,0:11:01.064
how you've always disliked Noble Consort Lumière.

0:11:01.400,0:11:05.920
But she has made many compromises
for the good of the Empress.

0:11:08.300,0:11:11.520
Your Majesty, I have no reason to harm Noble Consort Lumière.

0:11:12.270,0:11:14.699
For all these years that I've been managing the harem,

0:11:14.850,0:11:17.880
has Your Majesty ever seen me intentionally harm anyone?

0:11:18.240,0:11:19.680
You know it in your heart.

0:11:19.900,0:11:20.880
Your Majesty!

0:11:24.640,0:11:27.640
During the reign of Emperor Gaozong of Tang Dynasty,
Wu Meiniang was in high favor.

0:11:27.680,0:11:29.200
She wanted to take down Empress Wang,

0:11:29.240,0:11:32.433
so she strangled her own daughter in the cradle

0:11:32.790,0:11:35.236
and then accused Empress Wang of the murder.

0:11:35.410,0:11:39.080
My current predicament is the same as that of Empress Wang.

0:11:40.420,0:11:41.440
Your Majesty...

0:11:42.640,0:11:44.359
Her Majesty has placed her blame.

0:11:44.721,0:11:46.240
My own death would not be lamentable.

0:11:47.380,0:11:49.080
However, my child...

0:11:51.600,0:11:56.000
he did not even have the chance to open his eyes and see this world.

0:11:57.730,0:12:00.160
My child was innocent and died unjustly.

0:12:08.520,0:12:10.680
Longyue, why are you crying?

0:12:12.410,0:12:14.120
I did not see anything...

0:12:14.200,0:12:16.200
I did not see anything...

0:12:18.760,0:12:19.760
Come here.

0:12:22.000,0:12:24.030
What did you see? Tell your Imperial Father.

0:12:25.000,0:12:27.410
Imperial Father is here. You have nothing to fear.

0:12:28.880,0:12:30.120
Your Imperial Mother is here.

0:12:30.120,0:12:31.800
Tell Imperial Mother what happened.

0:12:32.040,0:12:34.080
Don't be afraid. Tell me.

0:12:35.280,0:12:37.480
Imperial Mother pushed Mother Lumière!

0:12:37.840,0:12:39.880
She pushed Mother Lumière!

0:12:40.520,0:12:42.640
Nonsense! You taught her to say that!

0:12:43.400,0:12:44.960
Say it! You taught her to defame me, didn't you!

0:12:45.400,0:12:47.600
Otherwise, it was you! Noble Consort Estime!

0:12:48.040,0:12:49.200
Your Majesty, you...

0:12:49.440,0:12:51.680
I'm wrongfully accused, Your Majesty.

0:12:52.040,0:12:53.280
This was an accident.

0:12:53.280,0:12:56.910
How could I have foreseen it and told Longyue to say that?

0:13:00.640,0:13:02.306
She is only six years old.

0:13:03.000,0:13:04.398
Is she capable of lying?

0:13:06.760,0:13:08.880
Besides, Noble Consort Lumière has just woken up.

0:13:09.000,0:13:10.351
Who could teach Longyue this lie?

0:13:10.560,0:13:11.560
Your Majesty!

0:13:12.080,0:13:16.200
I have been defamed just like Empress Wang.

0:13:16.480,0:13:18.186
I am not Emperor Gaozong.

0:13:18.400,0:13:20.000
I'm not fooled so easily!

0:13:20.200,0:13:22.930
You have always viewed Huan Huan as your mortal enemy.

0:13:23.000,0:13:24.820
You would be more than happy to eliminate her.

0:13:24.820,0:13:27.040
I swear in the names of my Ula-Nara ancestors,

0:13:27.400,0:13:31.200
I have never done anything to harm
Noble Consort Lumière's unborn child.

0:13:31.560,0:13:36.245
Why don't you take this oath in front of
the late Empress Dowager's Heavenly tablet?

0:13:37.800,0:13:41.880
The Empress has a vicious heart and cruelly harmed an imperial heir.

0:13:42.800,0:13:44.280
From this day onwards,

0:13:44.800,0:13:47.240
she is banned from stepping out of the Palace of Great Benevolence.

0:13:50.200,0:13:51.160
Su Peisheng.

0:13:51.280,0:13:52.120
Your Majesty.

0:13:52.200,0:13:53.200
Take her away.

0:13:53.600,0:13:54.520
Aye.

0:13:56.520,0:13:57.920
Your Majesty.

0:13:58.640,0:14:00.991
Please, Your Majesty.

0:14:23.500,0:14:26.290
Your Majesty, pardon me for asking.

0:14:26.840,0:14:28.571
Is it true that the Empress...

0:14:28.750,0:14:30.280
You have served as an official for a long time.

0:14:30.380,0:14:32.160
It's only right that you have concerns.

0:14:33.090,0:14:35.191
I have thoroughly investigated this matter.

0:14:35.760,0:14:37.467
The Empress has no defense.

0:14:38.050,0:14:38.880
Your Majesty.

0:14:39.430,0:14:43.751
Although the Empress is not as benevolent
as the late Empress Première,

0:14:43.940,0:14:45.720
Her Majesty is not a malicious person.

0:14:46.020,0:14:48.040
There were many other incidents in the past...

0:14:48.110,0:14:50.226
It's not that I didn't have my suspicions.

0:14:50.530,0:14:52.480
I just did not want to bother.

0:14:53.400,0:14:54.685
But as for this incident,

0:14:55.320,0:14:57.541
the Empress has no credible defense.

0:14:58.410,0:15:01.810
But why would Her Majesty go to such lengths?

0:15:02.000,0:15:03.841
"Desire is a ravine one cannot fill."

0:15:04.660,0:15:06.670
“A greedy heart is never satisfied."

0:15:07.080,0:15:08.591
Now she's the Empress,

0:15:08.790,0:15:11.160
so she expects to be the legitimate Empress Dowager.

0:15:12.510,0:15:14.361
I entrusted the Third Prince to her.

0:15:14.670,0:15:16.630
And it caused her to form improper ideas.

0:15:17.050,0:15:18.316
Your Majesty is wise.

0:15:18.720,0:15:20.224
Yet, whoever succeeds the throne,

0:15:20.680,0:15:23.590
Her Majesty will always be the Imperial Mother Empress Dowager.

0:15:24.270,0:15:27.010
How could she willingly let her power slip from her grasp?

0:15:28.020,0:15:30.980
Then... how does Your Majesty plan to proceed?

0:15:35.360,0:15:38.820
I have heard rumors are arising in the palace.

0:15:39.870,0:15:41.431
Claiming that many children

0:15:41.620,0:15:43.414
died at Her Majesty's hands.

0:15:44.000,0:15:46.740
But rumors are just rumors in the end.

0:15:47.290,0:15:50.160
Just as only the Empress will always be the Empress.

0:15:51.090,0:15:54.088
Changing the head of the harem will have 
a far-reaching impact.

0:15:55.260,0:15:57.102
My thoughts have not gone there yet.

0:15:57.430,0:16:00.540
A stable harem is a blessing to the Great Qing.

0:16:02.560,0:16:04.623
But I will ask the Empress to reflect on her wrongdoings,

0:16:05.680,0:16:06.821
and the punishment will be stern.

0:16:19.780,0:16:21.820
Your Highness, please have some tea and take a rest.

0:16:26.160,0:16:28.172
No matter how much I recite the sutras,

0:16:28.172,0:16:30.910
it cannot redeem my regret and shame for the child.

0:16:31.210,0:16:33.090
It was against Your Highness's own will.

0:16:37.050,0:16:38.488
The child is no more.

0:16:39.130,0:16:41.814
That is because his fate was only gently linked with that of Your Highness.

0:16:44.560,0:16:46.560
The most important matter at hand is that

0:16:47.100,0:16:48.923
although His Majesty has confined the Empress,

0:16:49.100,0:16:50.838
His Majesty did not announce any punishment.

0:16:51.060,0:16:52.940
The Empress is the foster mother of the Third Prince,

0:16:53.480,0:16:55.541
and a close relative of the late Empress Dowager.

0:16:56.280,0:16:57.968
For her to be pulled out by the roots,

0:16:59.490,0:17:01.592
we need to leave her with no one to rely on.

0:17:07.748,0:17:09.870
Mother, it's cold at night.

0:17:10.460,0:17:12.110
Kneeling can damage your health.

0:17:12.420,0:17:13.920
I have had this bird's nest soup made for you.

0:17:14.460,0:17:15.799
Please get up and have some.

0:17:17.920,0:17:19.630
I appreciate your filial heart.

0:17:24.876,0:17:27.815
I know that Mother is heartbroken over my unborn little brother.

0:17:28.480,0:17:30.400
My wife Fuca and I copied this sutra

0:17:30.600,0:17:31.566
to burn for him.

0:17:32.060,0:17:33.737
We wish he will soon enter the Pure Land.

0:17:35.150,0:17:36.829
You and Fuca have worked hard.

0:17:37.280,0:17:39.360
Mother, you're ill and I can't share your pain.

0:17:40.200,0:17:41.600
My heart is fuming with anxiety.

0:17:43.780,0:17:45.334
I know you're a filial son.

0:17:47.540,0:17:49.273
How has the Third Prince been?

0:17:50.120,0:17:52.979
I heard my Third Brother has been pleading with Imperial Father
 for mercy on Imperial Mother.

0:17:53.580,0:17:55.648
But Imperial Father scolded him.

0:17:57.630,0:18:01.670
The Third Prince ... was brought up by the Empress.

0:18:02.630,0:18:04.285
Now that the Empress is punished,

0:18:05.010,0:18:06.677
you should associate with him less.

0:18:06.970,0:18:07.630
Yes.

0:18:08.220,0:18:10.930
The Third Prince and Imperial Mother depend on each other

0:18:10.930,0:18:12.350
"as close as teeth and lips."

0:18:12.560,0:18:13.503
I understand.

0:18:13.980,0:18:14.986
Of course,

0:18:15.810,0:18:17.326
each day with the Empress

0:18:17.570,0:18:19.671
gives the Third Prince a chance to succeed to the throne.

0:18:20.490,0:18:25.020
And each day with the Third Prince
gives the Empress another layer of support.

0:18:25.530,0:18:27.650
Yes, I understand, Mother.

0:18:36.170,0:18:37.920
Fourth Brother, you've always been the most diligent.

0:18:37.920,0:18:39.630
Even after marriage, you don't ever relax.

0:18:39.630,0:18:41.400
How do you have leisure to stand around today?

0:18:41.670,0:18:43.125
Today is Eighth Uncle's birthday.

0:18:43.300,0:18:45.477
I went to visit him in the prison of the Imperial Clan Court.

0:18:46.680,0:18:48.502
You were so bold as to visit Eighth Uncle?

0:18:48.930,0:18:50.270
You weren't afraid of being seen?

0:18:50.270,0:18:51.831
I wouldn't tell if anyone else asks.

0:18:52.270,0:18:54.850
But as your younger brother, I wouldn't keep secrets from you.

0:18:55.900,0:18:58.180
So ... Has Eighth Uncle been well?

0:19:00.000,0:19:01.089
How can he be well?

0:19:01.280,0:19:03.270
He's imprisoned, living worse than death.

0:19:04.110,0:19:07.076
Third Brother, there's something I've always wanted to tell you,

0:19:07.432,0:19:08.835
but I wonder if it's appropriate.

0:19:08.870,0:19:10.980
We're brothers. Don't feel like a stranger. Tell me.

0:19:13.200,0:19:14.750
After the fight for the throne,

0:19:14.750,0:19:16.000
Imperial Father had numerous clansmen locked up.

0:19:16.120,0:19:17.740
Whether Eighth Uncle or Fourteenth Uncle,

0:19:18.080,0:19:20.000
they were both as close to Imperial Father as "arms and legs."

0:19:20.460,0:19:22.450
If we can intercede on behalf of our uncles

0:19:22.600,0:19:24.480
and have Imperial Father's mercy bestowed on them,

0:19:24.590,0:19:26.560
that would preserve Imperial Father's reputation -

0:19:27.050,0:19:29.646
and a century from now, people won't say he
"destroyed his own arms and legs."

0:19:30.180,0:19:32.220
Also, this will bring peace to
the Empress Dowager under the Nine Springs.

0:19:33.100,0:19:34.892
Next month is the birth anniversary of the prior emperor.

0:19:35.350,0:19:36.668
If I get the chance that day,

0:19:37.100,0:19:40.160
I want to plead for Imperial Father's pardon on 
Eighth Uncle and Fourteenth Uncle.

0:19:40.900,0:19:43.464
This is also the most filial tribute
to the late prior emperor and the Empress Dowager.

0:19:44.990,0:19:46.831
You have very noble intentions, Fourth Brother.

0:19:47.410,0:19:49.139
I'm so foolish, this didn't even cross my mind.

0:19:49.660,0:19:52.740
All right. If I get the chance on that day,

0:19:53.120,0:19:55.200
I'll certainly plead with Imperial Father for clemency.

0:19:55.660,0:19:56.391
Good.

0:19:58.881,0:20:00.000
Have some tea, Your Majesty.

0:20:03.170,0:20:07.260
His Majesty said you still can't go out yet.

0:20:08.640,0:20:10.694
Your Majesty has accompanied His Majesty for so many years...

0:20:10.970,0:20:12.680
but you were never confined.

0:20:13.680,0:20:17.420
Noble Consort Lumière enjoys high favor,
yet she's been confined many times.

0:20:18.650,0:20:21.730
I am the Empress. I can endure it.

0:20:21.956,0:20:23.000
[peace]

0:20:23.320,0:20:25.900
By the way, I heard that the Third Prince
interceded for Your Majesty

0:20:26.530,0:20:28.140
but invoked His Majesty's rebuke.

0:20:29.320,0:20:30.749
The Third Prince is truly stupid.

0:20:31.030,0:20:33.110
His priority right now should be protecting himself.

0:20:33.620,0:20:36.410
Your Majesty, the Third Prince was just being filial.

0:20:36.660,0:20:39.238
If a filial heart is misused, it can harm himself and others!

0:20:42.290,0:20:44.639
I can only hope that on the prior emperor's birth anniversary,

0:20:45.130,0:20:46.720
the Third Prince will meet my expectations.

0:20:48.470,0:20:50.276
As long as the Third Prince has a future,

0:20:50.840,0:20:53.090
all my suffering will not be in vain.

