0:21:24.420,0:21:26.512
You performed the task assigned well.

0:21:28.590,0:21:31.710
The prior emperor's ceremony was befitting.

0:21:33.970,0:21:35.316
Thank you for your praise, Imperial Father.

0:21:37.100,0:21:39.340
I saw the efforts you've made.

0:21:41.520,0:21:44.980
By the way, I heard that recently

0:21:45.480,0:21:47.970
you've visited your Eighth Uncle a few times.

0:21:49.150,0:21:50.060
Yes.

0:21:51.200,0:21:54.150
Eighth Uncle ... He is pitiful.

0:21:56.580,0:21:58.360
You do have benevolence residing in your heart.

0:21:59.500,0:22:02.030
Imperial Father, Eighth Uncle made a grave mistake.

0:22:02.670,0:22:04.382
Any punishment is justified.

0:22:04.960,0:22:07.046
It's just that all the sons of the prior emperor

0:22:07.300,0:22:08.932
are your brothers, like "arms and legs."

0:22:09.300,0:22:11.160
I think if the prior emperor were here,

0:22:11.630,0:22:14.800
he'd want to see filial piety and brotherly love.

0:22:16.550,0:22:17.550
What else?

0:22:17.930,0:22:18.892
And ...

0:22:19.810,0:22:20.984
And Fourteenth Uncle.

0:22:21.480,0:22:25.760
Imperial Father, Fourteenth Uncle is your brother by birth,
and the nearest uncle to me.

0:22:26.650,0:22:28.213
But he's been confined all this time.

0:22:28.610,0:22:30.020
When the prior emperor

0:22:30.304,0:22:31.937
confined Thirteenth Uncle,

0:22:32.110,0:22:34.230
you pleaded earnestly for him.

0:22:34.820,0:22:36.810
For the sake of the prior emperor,

0:22:37.490,0:22:39.350
what if you released Fourteenth Uncle?

0:22:41.000,0:22:42.853
I see you've been worrying about your uncles.

0:22:43.040,0:22:43.893
I dare not.

0:22:44.330,0:22:45.490
It's just that I heard ...

0:22:46.290,0:22:49.200
when the Empress Dowager was gravely ill,
she missed Fourteenth Uncle very much.

0:22:50.210,0:22:51.222
I was thinking

0:22:51.550,0:22:54.460
if Fourteenth Uncle were allowed to visit back then...

0:22:54.720,0:22:56.361
If your Fourteenth Uncle visited,

0:22:56.550,0:22:58.568
would the Empress Dowager's illness have been cured?

0:22:59.850,0:23:02.340
Do you think I'm unfilial to the Empress Dowager?

0:23:04.190,0:23:05.040
I don't dare.

0:23:05.140,0:23:06.050
You don't dare?

0:23:07.560,0:23:10.230
Weren't you just speaking of brotherly love?

0:23:11.190,0:23:12.339
I am not loving,

0:23:12.570,0:23:15.610
so no wonder my brothers don't respect me.

0:23:16.700,0:23:18.240
"When a father is loving, his son is filial."

0:23:18.870,0:23:20.157
I am not loving,

0:23:20.370,0:23:22.756
so there's no need for you to be filial?

0:23:23.290,0:23:24.544
That isn't what I meant.

0:23:25.870,0:23:26.754
Imperial Father.

0:23:27.580,0:23:30.170
I was thinking for your reputation.

0:23:31.550,0:23:32.554
Imperial Father,

0:23:33.050,0:23:35.012
whatever my uncles have done,

0:23:35.680,0:23:37.205
they are your brothers after all.

0:23:37.760,0:23:39.302
Whatever Imperial Mother has done,

0:23:39.680,0:23:40.972
she is still your wife.

0:23:41.970,0:23:44.024
I can withstand your momentary anger.

0:23:44.600,0:23:46.840
But I must think about your legacy down the centuries.

0:23:47.730,0:23:50.480
You've imprisoned your brothers and confined your wife.

0:23:50.770,0:23:51.869
The people are frightened -

0:23:53.070,0:23:54.589
what will your subjects think about you?

0:23:55.190,0:23:56.956
What will my subjects think?

0:23:58.870,0:23:59.908
It seems that

0:24:00.398,0:24:02.473
you want to be my master now.

0:24:04.040,0:24:05.664
I am your Imperial Father.

0:24:06.410,0:24:08.099
Yet you can't discern right from wrong

0:24:08.330,0:24:10.870
and vehemently defend guilty men and women.

0:24:11.670,0:24:12.660
In your eyes,

0:24:12.960,0:24:14.170
am I such a tyrant?

0:24:15.090,0:24:17.420
Or you cannot tolerate my rule

0:24:17.760,0:24:19.300
and can't wait to replace me?

0:24:19.640,0:24:21.000
I dare not, I dare not!

0:24:21.350,0:24:22.231
I dare not!

0:24:22.680,0:24:24.135
When I had just ascended the throne,

0:24:24.890,0:24:26.510
your Eighth Uncle and Fourteenth Uncle

0:24:27.440,0:24:29.720
disrespected me and found fault with everything I did.

0:24:30.150,0:24:31.850
You saw it all very well!

0:24:33.270,0:24:35.440
Yet today, you've switched sides and turned against me.

0:24:35.820,0:24:37.751
You're interceding for those who wished to harm me.

0:24:39.360,0:24:42.200
You've joined their "filthy breath" to disobey me.

0:24:45.040,0:24:48.650
As for why I confined your Imperial Mother,

0:24:50.120,0:24:52.540
it was not only for Noble Consort Lumiere's unborn son.

0:24:54.000,0:24:57.370
Your Imperial Mother has been pulling many threads

0:24:57.970,0:25:00.000
hoping to make you the Crown Prince!

0:25:06.241,0:25:07.230
Imperial Father...

0:25:07.230,0:25:08.793
So you still call me Father!

0:25:09.730,0:25:11.104
You are my eldest son.

0:25:11.270,0:25:13.140
Although you lack strength and competence,

0:25:14.320,0:25:17.920
I have always taught you and been forgiving towards you.

0:25:19.280,0:25:20.642
Heaven had no mercy.

0:25:21.030,0:25:23.039
I've made you become someone else's son!

0:25:23.370,0:25:25.145
If you want to plead for your Eighth Uncle,

0:25:25.450,0:25:26.759
why don't you be his son?

0:25:28.370,0:25:29.268
Imperial Father,

0:25:30.830,0:25:32.171
however angry you are,

0:25:33.540,0:25:34.750
you wouldn't disown your own son.

0:25:35.000,0:25:36.559
It was you who abandoned me as your father.

0:25:36.840,0:25:38.146
Not the other way around!

0:25:40.170,0:25:41.510
- Su Peisheng!
- Your Majesty.

0:25:41.680,0:25:45.090
Announce my decree:
Hongshi lacks the integrity to stay in the palace.

0:25:46.600,0:25:48.510
Since he is loyal to Yunsi,

0:25:49.480,0:25:51.694
he will become Yunsi's son.

0:25:52.400,0:25:55.350
Due to his crimes, Yunsi was stripped of his Imperial Belt

0:25:55.860,0:25:57.440
and his name was removed from the imperial pedigree.

0:25:57.940,0:25:59.551
Hongshi, as his son,

0:26:00.150,0:26:01.923
must also lose his Imperial Belt.

0:26:02.160,0:26:04.610
Immediately confiscate Hongshi's Imperial Belt.

0:26:05.240,0:26:07.400
His Eighth Uncle Lord Heng will foster and discipline him.

0:26:08.040,0:26:10.490
I no longer have this son!

0:26:11.410,0:26:12.200
Your Majesty...

0:26:12.200,0:26:13.506
What are you waiting for!

0:26:15.290,0:26:16.320
I obey.

0:26:38.730,0:26:39.720
Your Majesty!

0:26:39.820,0:26:40.680
Terrible news.

0:26:41.440,0:26:42.480
What is it now?

0:26:42.610,0:26:43.600
Third Prince, he...

0:26:43.780,0:26:44.890
He misspoke today?

0:26:45.660,0:26:47.990
It doesn't matter if His Majesty keeps me confined for now.

0:26:48.330,0:26:50.610
What matters is he still considers my sister,

0:26:51.370,0:26:54.143
and that gives me the chance to rise again like the sun.

0:26:54.750,0:26:56.804
His Majesty stripped the Third Prince of his Imperial Belt

0:26:57.460,0:26:59.033
and made him the son of Lord VIII!

0:27:00.000,0:27:01.453
What are you talking about?

0:27:01.630,0:27:03.120
The Imperial Clan Court has received the decree.

0:27:03.880,0:27:04.837
Nonsense!

0:27:06.140,0:27:07.993
The Third Prince is His Majesty's son.

0:27:08.390,0:27:09.767
How is this possible?

0:27:10.470,0:27:11.840
I wouldn't dare lie to Your Majesty.

0:27:12.060,0:27:14.492
The Third Prince spoke up for Lord XIV, Lord VIII, and Your Majesty.

0:27:15.060,0:27:16.970
His Majesty accused him of having ulterior motives.

0:27:19.480,0:27:24.320
Why all of a sudden ... did he speak up for those traitors?

0:27:26.160,0:27:29.320
All my years of painstaking efforts ... completely wasted...

0:27:30.120,0:27:31.280
Completely wasted!

0:27:31.660,0:27:33.740
Your Majesty, please think of a way to save the Third Prince!

0:27:33.960,0:27:35.106
It's no use!

0:27:37.080,0:27:38.827
His Majesty has always been hard-hearted.

0:27:39.380,0:27:43.290
He has cut off his paternal love by doing so....

0:27:47.760,0:27:48.734
Your Majesty,

0:27:49.850,0:27:51.560
if the Third Prince can't be the Crown...

0:27:51.560,0:27:52.989
Without the Third Prince,

0:27:52.989,0:27:55.200
there is still the Fourth Prince and Fifth Prince.

0:27:55.730,0:27:58.010
At the worst, there is the Sixth Prince.

0:27:58.954,0:28:00.134
The Sixth Prince...

0:28:00.134,0:28:02.310
Just like how Consort Austuce died.

0:28:02.980,0:28:04.129
Without Zhen Huan,

0:28:04.990,0:28:06.940
I can adopt the Sixth Prince.

0:28:08.660,0:28:10.860
Nothing else matters. Nothing!

0:28:12.030,0:28:14.320
As long as I am the Empress,

0:28:15.200,0:28:18.450
I can rise again like the sun behind the mountains!

0:28:19.630,0:28:21.210
It doesn't matter who gave birth!

0:28:22.670,0:28:24.356
As long as the child becomes mine,

0:28:25.550,0:28:28.670
I will be the one and only Empress Dowager!

0:28:47.320,0:28:48.810
Did you prepare what I asked for?

0:28:49.110,0:28:50.320
I did prepare it.

0:28:50.570,0:28:52.560
But Her Majesty isn't aware of this.

0:28:52.910,0:28:54.330
Shouldn't we report to her?

0:28:54.330,0:28:56.320
A suffering master indicates the servant's incompetence.

0:28:57.620,0:28:59.400
I've followed Her Majesty for so many years,

0:28:59.500,0:29:01.313
and she has never endured such indignity.

0:29:02.500,0:29:05.120
A lofty Empress is confined by a concubine's set-up?

0:29:05.920,0:29:08.480
It even caused Her Majesty to lose the Third Prince.

0:29:09.050,0:29:10.660
There can't be such injustice under Heaven.

0:29:11.090,0:29:13.380
But this is too risky. Should we fail,

0:29:13.600,0:29:15.090
our lives will be at stake.

0:29:16.520,0:29:18.227
It doesn't matter even if I lose my life.

0:29:19.270,0:29:20.996
As long as I can get rid of Noble Consort Lumière,

0:29:21.560,0:29:23.200
Her Majesty will be at peace from now on.

0:29:24.440,0:29:25.489
Give it to me.

0:29:43.130,0:29:44.170
Seventeenth Brother.

0:29:45.250,0:29:47.740
The ceremony for Imperial Father's birth anniversary is complete.

0:29:49.510,0:29:55.680
Whenever I remember our days with Imperial Father,

0:29:57.180,0:29:58.720
I feel deeply touched.

0:30:00.770,0:30:02.444
And so I shed tears today.

0:30:04.110,0:30:06.940
As a family, we are here to celebrate our brotherly bond.

0:30:09.690,0:30:11.074
I thank Your Majesty for your care.

0:30:11.240,0:30:12.320
I raise a toast to you.

0:30:12.320,0:30:14.190
Sit down, sit down.

0:30:15.740,0:30:17.607
We're one family. Don't stand on ceremony.

0:30:18.990,0:30:20.480
If Imperial Father was here

0:30:22.540,0:30:25.680
and saw you having a child on the way now,

0:30:27.090,0:30:28.640
he'd be delighted.

0:30:30.340,0:30:32.901
Everything I have is by the grace of Your Majesty.

0:30:36.600,0:30:40.460
I always feel grateful for the prior emperor's edification.

0:30:42.180,0:30:45.520
And you always show respect to your elder brother

0:30:46.690,0:30:48.480
while performing duties as a court official.

0:30:49.570,0:30:50.740
This is what's called

0:30:51.990,0:30:56.150
"harmony between brothers, as well as monarch and subject."

0:30:59.870,0:31:00.640
Yes.

0:31:12.210,0:31:14.400
Your little cousin is in aunty's belly.

0:31:15.840,0:31:17.200
Sixth Prince, do you like him?

0:31:17.300,0:31:18.790
I want a little sister.

0:31:23.430,0:31:24.768
What about Your Lordship?

0:31:26.400,0:31:27.395
Either is good.

0:31:34.450,0:31:38.150
Hongyan is very fond of Meng's child.

0:31:39.160,0:31:40.416
They seem to be fated.

0:31:42.370,0:31:44.712
It's natural to have a close affinity between cousins.

0:31:46.960,0:31:49.200
Hongyan, Hongyan.

0:31:49.590,0:31:51.769
Come to Mother to have some soup.

0:31:52.340,0:31:53.760
Don't disturb Lady Xian anymore.

0:31:53.760,0:31:56.120
I want my aunty to feed me. I want my aunty to feed me.

0:31:56.590,0:31:58.250
Sure, aunty will feed you.

0:31:58.470,0:31:59.344
Good boy.

0:32:24.580,0:32:25.454
Jingxian!

0:32:26.250,0:32:27.410
Jingxian, what's wrong?

0:32:27.920,0:32:28.640
Jingxian!

0:32:28.750,0:32:30.080
Imperial doctors!

0:32:30.540,0:32:31.680
Call for the doctors now!

0:32:33.090,0:32:34.269
What's going on?

0:32:34.420,0:32:35.773
She was fine just now.

0:32:36.920,0:32:37.630
Yes.

0:32:39.220,0:32:40.844
She seems to be poisoned.

0:32:42.720,0:32:43.837
The food has been poisoned.

0:32:44.060,0:32:45.600
Imperial guards! Attend His Majesty!

0:32:47.350,0:32:49.203
Your Majesty, if Lady Xian was poisoned,

0:32:49.400,0:32:51.190
it's best if Your Majesty leaves for the Hall of Mental Cultivation.

0:32:51.200,0:32:52.147
Your Majesty.

0:32:52.650,0:32:53.760
I will not leave.

0:32:55.480,0:32:58.128
I'll stay to see whoever was so bold

0:32:58.128,0:33:00.640
as to assassinate her in my presence.

0:33:02.490,0:33:03.580
Move her to the back chamber first.

0:33:03.580,0:33:04.320
Yes.

0:33:23.600,0:33:25.550
Your Lordship...

0:33:27.100,0:33:28.510
I'm here. Right here.

0:33:28.850,0:33:29.590
Your Lordship.

0:33:31.520,0:33:32.100
Your Lordship.

0:33:32.730,0:33:33.340
Hurry.

0:33:43.160,0:33:44.072
Silver needle.

0:33:51.670,0:33:52.777
It's Crane's Red Crown.

0:33:54.790,0:33:55.802
Crane's Red Crown?

0:33:56.050,0:33:58.000
No. Her Ladyship's pregnancy is already full-term.

0:33:58.420,0:34:00.226
Quick. Go prepare the labor-inducing herbs.

0:34:00.380,0:34:01.750
Hurry. Go quickly.

0:34:01.970,0:34:04.526
Your Lordship. Please allow me to take Her Ladyship's pulse.

0:34:13.350,0:34:15.196
Fortunately, Her Ladyship only consumed
a small amount of the poisoned food

0:34:15.400,0:34:16.614
and still has strength for labor.

0:34:16.770,0:34:18.230
Your Lordship, please ease your mind.

0:34:18.530,0:34:20.000
We doctors will take care of everything.

0:34:20.360,0:34:21.820
I will go report back to His Majesty.

0:34:22.110,0:34:22.952
Go quickly.

0:34:25.740,0:34:27.110
Your Lordship.

0:34:28.290,0:34:30.000
Who wants to harm me?

0:34:36.889,0:34:38.499
Your Majesty,

0:34:38.499,0:34:40.457
Lord Consort Xian consumed Crane's Red Crown.

0:34:45.260,0:34:48.550
How can that be mixed into a palace banquet?

0:34:51.730,0:34:53.930
What was the last thing Lady Consort Xian consumed?

0:34:58.610,0:34:59.985
Your Majesty,

0:35:00.438,0:35:02.973
Lady Consort Xian had some of the Sixth Prince's soup.

0:35:06.570,0:35:07.490
Jinxi.

0:35:24.430,0:35:26.493
The silver turned black. This soup is poisonous.

0:35:27.850,0:35:28.877
Test this bowl too.

0:35:39.060,0:35:40.251
This soup is also poisonous.

0:35:43.900,0:35:47.440
Your Majesty, someone wants to kill Hongyan and me.

0:35:48.320,0:35:50.000
Lord Consort Xian's poisoning was unintended.

0:35:52.750,0:35:53.926
I am here.

0:35:56.120,0:35:57.509
Go.

0:35:58.400,0:36:00.022
Go investigate!

0:36:00.960,0:36:07.500
How was such filth added to the food for
Noble Consort Lumière and the Sixth Prince?!

0:36:08.550,0:36:09.470
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:36:10.470,0:36:11.356
Your Lordship.

0:36:13.310,0:36:16.340
Am I about to die?

0:36:17.440,0:36:19.270
Nonsense. The imperial doctors are all here.

0:36:19.810,0:36:20.847
They're all here.

0:36:24.490,0:36:29.439
Your Lordship, it was because I got you drunk...

0:36:30.533,0:36:32.649
that gave me this child.

0:36:34.120,0:36:35.499
Don't talk about that now.

0:36:35.950,0:36:37.117
I will stay here with you.

0:36:37.790,0:36:39.250
I will always stay by your side.

0:36:43.500,0:36:46.000
Your Majesty, I have investigated thoroughly.

0:36:46.800,0:36:50.590
The dessert soup was made by the Imperial Kitchen 
and brought here by the servants.

0:36:51.140,0:36:54.260
The maid who brought the soup for
Noble Consort Lumière and the Sixth Prince

0:36:54.560,0:36:57.159
said she met the maid Autumn
from The Palace of Great Benevolence.

0:36:57.350,0:37:00.760
Autumn did open up the box and asked what was inside.

0:37:01.060,0:37:02.902
Besides Autumn, the maid did not see anyone else.

0:37:03.230,0:37:05.140
I have already brought Autumn here.

0:37:05.440,0:37:06.240
Bring her in.

0:37:06.360,0:37:06.940
Yes.

0:37:28.300,0:37:29.540
Who ordered you to do this?

0:37:33.390,0:37:36.000
Who ordered you to do this?

0:37:37.270,0:37:38.220
No one did.

0:37:39.430,0:37:41.041
It was my own doing.

0:37:42.400,0:37:43.350
Was it the Empress?

0:37:45.650,0:37:47.230
Her Majesty is still in confinement

0:37:48.110,0:37:49.650
and is not aware of my doings.

0:37:52.490,0:37:54.100
All of this was my own idea.

0:38:01.500,0:38:02.797
She's attempting suicide!

0:38:05.880,0:38:09.000
Your Majesty, why do you not believe Her Majesty?

0:38:10.510,0:38:13.420
Her Majesty is your wife! She loves you wholeheartedly.

0:38:13.590,0:38:18.250
Send her to the Department of Penalty
and punish her until she speaks the truth!

0:38:18.520,0:38:20.619
Your Majesty, Her Majesty is your wife!
The Empress of the Great Qing.

0:38:20.850,0:38:25.590
Your Majesty, why do you refuse to believe Her Majesty?

0:38:26.230,0:38:27.204
Carry her out.

0:38:27.690,0:38:29.780
Noble Consort Lumière, aren't you afraid of karmic retribution?

0:38:29.780,0:38:32.560
Noble Consort Lumière, you will die in hell!

0:38:33.280,0:38:35.110
You wretch, Noble Consort Lumière!

0:38:35.740,0:38:37.570
You wretch!

0:38:51.550,0:38:54.290
Your Majesty, it's a State Heir Prince.

0:38:55.260,0:38:57.843
But Lord Consort Xian was too weak after labor.

0:38:58.220,0:39:01.010
She was overcome by the poison and has just passed away.

0:39:22.330,0:39:23.190
Autumn.

0:39:25.540,0:39:26.376
Your Majesty.

0:39:27.210,0:39:28.179
Where's Autumn?

0:39:29.000,0:39:30.240
I haven't seen her around.

0:39:31.090,0:39:32.950
Even Jiang Fuhai is nowhere to be found.

0:39:33.510,0:39:35.590
Does Your Majesty want some water?
I can go pour some for you.

0:39:36.050,0:39:37.619
I'm asking you questions.

0:39:37.883,0:39:40.480
Why are you evading the question?

0:39:42.850,0:39:45.640
What else is there that I can't withstand?

0:39:46.480,0:39:48.329
Madam Autumn hasn't come back since yesterday.

0:39:48.690,0:39:50.520
Mr. Jiang has was also taken away last night.

0:39:50.730,0:39:51.614
How dare they!

0:39:52.280,0:39:56.810
How can they take away my servants
without sending half a word to me?

0:39:57.320,0:40:00.900
Your Majesty, the Department of Penalty
took them away per His Majesty's decree.

0:40:01.410,0:40:03.221
They said there was no need to inform Your Majesty.

0:40:05.870,0:40:07.412
What on earth has happened?

0:40:07.750,0:40:08.929
I also don't know.

0:40:09.460,0:40:13.000
I only heard Madam Autumn did not succeed
in poisoning Noble Consort Lumière

0:40:13.710,0:40:15.360
and killed Lord Consort Xian instead.

0:40:18.930,0:40:21.540
Are you still unwilling to tell the truth despite the whipping?

0:40:24.140,0:40:25.831
What is there to confess?

0:40:27.020,0:40:28.628
Her Majesty didn't do anything.

0:40:29.150,0:40:32.935
Do you really think His Majesty will believe you
if your tortures force a confession out of me?

0:40:33.940,0:40:39.110
Her Majesty will not spare you idiots once she regains power.

0:40:40.120,0:40:42.120
We received His Majesty's decree.

0:40:42.490,0:40:45.490
We won't spare any means to get the truth out of you.

0:40:47.040,0:40:49.160
Even if your body is made of steel,

0:40:50.580,0:40:53.224
I doubt you can withstand unrelenting instruments of torture.

0:40:53.750,0:40:54.974
Since you wouldn't tell us,

0:40:55.130,0:40:57.040
bring on the needle punishment!

0:40:57.380,0:40:58.220
How dare you!

0:40:58.220,0:41:00.080
Dare is not a question for us.

0:41:01.220,0:41:07.760
You need to ask if this needle dares to drill into your slim fingers.

0:41:09.060,0:41:11.390
Autumn is the most tight-lipped. She'll go first.

0:41:11.880,0:41:13.880
Let go of me! Let go of me!

0:41:20.990,0:41:22.477
That's what you get for not telling.

0:41:23.530,0:41:24.429
What about you?

0:41:26.040,0:41:28.120
You going to confess? Speak!

0:41:30.290,0:41:31.256
Hurry up and speak.

0:41:32.210,0:41:35.040
I wonder if the servants will confess.

0:41:37.420,0:41:40.880
I've heard the Brilliant Madams are even more capable
than the men in the Ministry of Justice.

0:41:42.760,0:41:47.510
But Autumn has always been the most loyal to the Empress.

0:41:47.796,0:41:49.769
I'm afraid she won't confess.

0:41:50.810,0:41:52.614
Even if she doesn't, there is still Jiang Fuhai.

0:41:53.150,0:41:54.400
And besides Jiang Fuhai,

0:41:55.110,0:41:57.246
 Spring is also serving her time at the Department of Penalty.

0:41:57.860,0:41:59.360
Having them interrogated one after the other,

0:41:59.360,0:42:00.820
someone will eventually open up.

0:42:01.610,0:42:03.339
And once torn open,

0:42:03.881,0:42:06.070
everything they've hidden inside will be revealed.

0:42:06.870,0:42:09.950
My mind is finally at ease after hearing that.

0:42:11.750,0:42:13.737
This will become even more chaotic.

0:42:14.080,0:42:16.450
His Majesty must be struck at his most vulnerable spot.

0:42:16.920,0:42:20.170
Otherwise, if the Empress turns the tide around, 
it won't be easy for us to reverse it.

